---

<Base title="Ganadores 2025" description="Los ganadores del Mundial de Salsa y Bachata de La Negra Dance Festival 2025." lang="es">
  <SubNav items={subNav} label="Secciones de la competición" />

  <div class="prop">
    <!-- INTRO -->
    <section class="p-section p-center winners-intro">
      <div class="p-container">
        <p class="p-eyebrow">Salsa y Bachata</p>
        <h1 class="p-display">Los ganadores de 2025</h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WINNERS GRID -->
    <section class="p-section p-gray winners">
      <div class="p-container winners-grid">
        {categories.map((c) => (
          <article class="winner-card">
            {c.video ? (
              <button class="winner-img has-video" type="button" data-video={c.video} aria-label={`Ver vídeo del campeón: ${c.title}`}>
                <img src={img(c.image)} alt={c.title} loading="lazy" />
                <span class="winner-play" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg></span>
              </button>
            ) : (
              <div class="winner-img"><img src={img(c.image)} alt={c.title} loading="lazy" /></div>
            )}
            <h2 class="winner-title">{c.title}</h2>
            <ol class="podium">
              {c.podium.map((p, i) => <li class={`pos-${i + 1}`}>{p}</li>)}
            </ol>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- GALLERY -->
    <section class="p-section">
      <div class="p-container gallery-grid">
        {gallery.map((src) => <div class="gallery-item"><img src={img(src)} alt="" loading="lazy" /></div>)}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FINAL CTA -->
    <section class="p-section">
      <div class="p-container">
        <div class="final-card p-center">
          <p class="p-eyebrow">Disfruta bailando</p>
          <h2 class="p-h2 p-white">Tu festival de baile latino</h2>
          <p class="final-text">Tres días de salsa y bachata, para los enamorados-as del baile latino. Puro fuego en la pista: artistas, concursantes, talleres, fiesta y mucho ritmo. No te lo puedes perder, del 21 al 25 de octubre del 2026 en Calpe (España).</p>

          <p>Un festival y concurso de baile a nivel internacional de Salsa y Bachata.</p>
          <p class="cta-claim">¡Ven, baila y disfruta!</p>
          <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a class="p-btn p-btn-light" href="/tu-pase/">Comprar Pase</a>
            <span class="reg-closed"><span class="btn btn-solid btn-off" aria-disabled="true" role="button" title="Inscripciones cerradas">Inscríbete al Mundial</span><span class="reg-note">Inscripciones cerradas: el plazo de inscripción al Mundial 2026 ha finalizado.</span></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <VideoModal />
</Base>

<style>
  .winners-intro { padding-bottom: clamp(20px, 3vw, 34px); }

  /* WINNERS GRID */
  .winners-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 44px 28px; }
  .winner-card { text-align: left; }
  .winner-img { position: relative; border-radius: 18px; overflow: hidden; aspect-ratio: 4/3; margin-bottom: 18px; background: var(--p-card); }
  .winner-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  button.winner-img { display: block; width: 100%; padding: 0; border: 0; background: var(--p-ink); cursor: pointer; }
  button.winner-img img { transition: transform .4s ease, opacity .2s; }
  button.winner-img:hover img { transform: scale(1.05); opacity: .92; }
  .winner-play {
    position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 54px; height: 54px; border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(220, 30, 40, .92); color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, .35);
    transition: transform .2s, background .2s;
  }
  .winner-play svg { width: 26px; height: 26px; margin-left: 2px; }
  button.winner-img:hover .winner-play { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.08); background: rgb(220, 30, 40); }
  .winner-title {
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.4vw, 20px); letter-spacing: .04em; color: var(--gold); margin: 0 0 14px;
  }
  .podium { list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  .podium li { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--p-muted); padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--p-line); }
  .podium li:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
  .podium .pos-1 { font-weight: 700; color: var(--p-ink); }

  /* GALLERY */
  .gallery-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 16px; }
  .gallery-item { border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; aspect-ratio: 1/1; background: var(--p-card); }
  .gallery-item img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }

  /* FINAL CTA */
  .final-card {
    background: radial-gradient(120% 120% at 50% 0%, #211c33 0%, #0f0b1e 65%);
    border-radius: 26px;
    padding: clamp(40px, 6vw, 84px) clamp(24px, 5vw, 64px);
    color: #fff;
  }
  .final-card .p-eyebrow { color: var(--gold); }
  .final-text { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto 24px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .8); }
  .final-card > p { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .82); }
  .cta-claim { font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -.02em; color: #fff; font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 30px); margin: 6px 0 24px; }
  .cta-buttons { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; align-items: flex-start; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .winners-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 40px 24px; }
    .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .winners-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  }
</style>
